{"tid":842366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"棄藍天保經濟　北京或再現霧霾","createTime":"2018-09-30T09:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T08:24:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c121326e76622b3fdd4445e80cb1839c181d7f7e","tid":842366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180930/20511332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F20511332&d=Wm750lrdtaPfKF5rJEqd0oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=59b59d3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F20511332&h=f0d8f2bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180930/20511332</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月30日 <br />\n<br />\n棄藍天保經濟　北京或再現霧霾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180930/large/a1005a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180930%2Flarge%2Fa1005a.gif&h=6a950885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近年內地致力打「藍天保衞戰」，但在中美貿戰下不得不暫緩！當局日前下修京津冀等華北地區秋冬季的排放污染物目標，並且放寬鋼鐵、建材等高排放工業的生產限制，容許延長開工時間，勢令霧霾（圖）再現。有分析相信，這是在貿戰持續升溫下，當局逼不得已的做法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下調減排目標<br />\n<br />\n生態環境部聯同北京、天津、河北、河南、山東、山西6省市，共同制訂2018至2019年秋冬大氣污染治理方案，要求由10月1日至明年3月底，京津冀及周邊26個城巿的微細懸浮粒（PM2.5）平均濃度目標，要較去年同期下降3%，重度及以上污染天數較去年同期減少3%。<br />\n<br />\n比較去年的方案，當時政府要求的PM2.5平均濃度，要較去年同期下降15%以上，而較早前的徵求意見稿中亦曾提出5%的目標，可以見到減排力度明顯下調。方案亦提出，取消統一的停產限制，可適當縮短或延長開工時間，嚴禁「一刀切」，污染排放績效較好的企業更可以不限產。<br />\n<br />\n新浪財經指，PM2.5目標下調，應有考慮到宏觀經濟形勢偏弱、貿易磨擦不確定性等因素，且市場普遍對經濟較悲觀。廣州中山大學經濟系教授林江認為，下調目標與貿易戰有直接關係，「對地方政府而言是不得已而為之的做法&hellip;&hellip;如果有關部門堅持比較高的要求，很可能這些企業就乾脆結業了」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/自由亞洲電台  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n王毅杯子喻中美：打碎易　復原難<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n津警疑包庇黑心商販濫捕　12萬候鳥谷肥變野味"},{"pid":"d99984d08fb61108777cd3b9aa83e439962f21cc","tid":842366,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"生產嚟做乜撚"},{"pid":"fbad43eb568f2bd2516acc4bda96677db9a431a0","tid":842366,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"外資都走左，仲有用咩"},{"pid":"45b76caaa0d88147763210fc46c3664c4d2ab98f","tid":842366,"uid":25059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"唔係話產能過剩咩 仲生產咁多鋼鐵做咩？"},{"pid":"3f57bec6b3a73bbfcee6d2fd99ec921d958e41da","tid":842366,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbad43eb568f2bd2516acc4bda96677db9a431a0","tid":842366,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"外資都走左，仲有用咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"賣比非洲佬掛"},{"pid":"3c9a8b670eecdb39df871b1d62af2dedade31b1b","tid":842366,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"神未曾應許天空常藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1fe1c14dd8c13b2b0dff228165916103227ef4","tid":842366,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d99984d08fb61108777cd3b9aa83e439962f21cc","tid":842366,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"生產嚟做乜撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"咪係，出口美國又重稅<br />\n再補貼又畀人圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dba638e8710e737a9abee2e1a951010bf2b2d0","tid":842366,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"一於24小時開工不停放污染物破壞大氣層同全球人攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n贏國又贏<img 